stylometry: Data mining is an extremely important process.  Businesses have vast amounts of raw data that needs to be mined (organized so that it can be understood) in order to be useful.  Mining the date requires searching through it and finding trends that can be used to predict future trends, market values, demands, etc.  Many trends the business needs to know may be able to be found through searching through data, finding trends and organizing them, which is data mining.
